<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢١٨٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5577">أَبُو مُعَاوِيَةَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2571">الشَّيْبَانِيِّ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4458">عِكْرِمَةَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«نَهَى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنِ الْمُحَاقَلَةِ وَالْمُزَابَنَةِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>